{
  "text": "Haplotypes for ApoE isoforms 2, 3 and 4 were determined from base c.388 in codon 130 (T/C) and c.526 in codon 176 (T/C) (ref. sequence: NCBI36: 19: 50100279: 50105089: 1), which correspond to codon 112 and 158 in the earlier literature [CITATION_1] .",
